Legacy static ICS files (MVDcal_*.ics) are no longer generated.

Personal calendar subscriptions use on-demand ical.php?t={activeLink} (MELD-127).
Single-appointment download remains download-ics.php (session).

On deploy: delete any leftover calendars/MVDcal_*.ics on the server and disable
cron jobs that called cmd=calendar / rebuildCalendars().
